data.text:
Bio: when Juvia & Gray married, they have a baby named Aisu, they're days full of hapiness. 
But someday, when Aisu turned to 2, they're house was bombed by someone who has a revenge to Gray, that day Gray and Juvia was out for buying a present for Aisu and Aisu was left home. 
When they got home, they found their house was burned, and they can't found Aisu. They searched with police and their friends for 3 months and still can't find Aisu, then the police give up and claimed that Aisu was died because the bomb, then Gray never smiled once since that day.
5 years later, on Aisu's birthday,  at the fairy tail guild, there's a little girl that came, she said she was searching for Gray Fullbuster, when Gray notice the girl, he rushed to her and hugged her tight. He was know that, that girl was Aisu that lost 5 years ago. When all the Fairy tail's member heared it, they had a party for the long gone Aisu that came back.
Then Aisu told her story to all of the guild's member, that 5 years ago, when the bomb landed on the house, she was thrown to the river near their house.
When she woke up, she feel warm, she noticed that she was warmed by a dragon. That dragon named Icelyn (Aizuriin) the ice dragon. Icelyn raise & teach Aisu Dragon slayer magic. Then 4 years later Icelyn told her to go back to her real parents, so Aisu searched her parents with the guidance of her pendant that had a fairy tail's mark and his father's name. 
After she came back, Gray started to smile again and the guild back to normal with a new member.. (I'm sorry that the story is very long, and if the english is wrong -__-")
